- Yes!

291
00:13:12,024 --> 00:13:12,984
How dare you!

292
00:13:12,984 --> 00:13:14,424
I told you to seize Lu Zhen'er,

293
00:13:14,424 --> 00:13:15,664
not me!

294
00:13:19,024 --> 00:13:20,824
So you are the poisoner.

295
00:13:22,424 --> 00:13:23,944
How vicious!

296
00:13:23,944 --> 00:13:25,064
You planned this!

297
00:13:25,664 --> 00:13:27,344
Qiansichan's impact was severe.

298
00:13:27,344 --> 00:13:29,864
Neither His Majesty nor I believed
it was coincidence.

299
00:13:29,864 --> 00:13:32,104
So we had to find the poisoner.

300
00:13:32,864 --> 00:13:33,504
Witch!

301
00:13:39,424 --> 00:13:41,584
You schemed against me with Lu Zhen'er.

302
00:13:41,704 --> 00:13:44,144
I wished to restore peace to the harem.

303
00:13:44,264 --> 00:13:45,424
I never poisoned anyone!

304
00:13:45,744 --> 00:13:47,264
But even if I did,

305
00:13:47,704 --> 00:13:49,584
what could you do about it?

306
00:13:49,824 --> 00:13:51,464
You're unwell.

307
00:13:51,464 --> 00:13:53,704
Seems you must retire
to the Changle Temple.

308
00:13:53,984 --> 00:13:54,624
Outrageous!

309
00:13:55,184 --> 00:13:56,504
You dare curse me?

310
00:13:56,864 --> 00:13:59,344
I'll never go to the Changle Temple.

311
00:13:59,624 --> 00:14:01,344
Don't even think about driving me away.

312
00:14:04,344 --> 00:14:04,984
Your Majesty.

313
00:14:05,464 --> 00:14:06,464
What's wrong?

314
00:14:07,744 --> 00:14:08,744
Don't touch me!

315
00:14:14,064 --> 00:14:15,264
Summon the physician!

316
00:14:21,304 --> 00:14:23,424
(My period hasn't come this month.)

317
00:14:23,424 --> 00:14:26,304
(Lately, I can't eat and feel nauseous.)

318
00:14:26,304 --> 00:14:27,184
(Could it be...)

319
00:14:29,984 --> 00:14:31,424
I'm pregnant!

320
00:14:48,672 --> 00:14:53,400
♪Moonlight beyond the pass sighs
for restless fluttering petals♪

321
